metadata.name: #1 - Reykjavik Harbor
metadata.description:
This photograph was taken when I was in high school and IcelandAir was a cheap way to fly to Europe, at the "cost" of a layover in Reykjavik.

The photograph is of the harbor in Reykjavik. It was taken with an AE-1 film camera and scanned with Kodakâ€™s PhotoCD system. It is basically untouched since then.

It is the genesis piece of 6529 Raw and my genesis art NFT.
